## Setup

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Add data files to `data/`:
- `CPS - 2020-2025.gz` — IPUMS CPS ASEC extract
- `Subsector.xlsx` — Census BTOS subsector data

## Run

```python
from src.ipums_pipeline import IPUMSPipeline
from src.btos_pipeline import BTOSPipeline

cps = IPUMSPipeline("data/CPS - 2020-2025.gz")
cps.run()

btos = BTOSPipeline("data/Subsector.xlsx")
btos.run()
```

Or open `notebooks/labor_lens_analysis.py` in Google Colab.

